-- Academics in Australia Win 16% Pay Increase Over 3 Years, Review Reports
-- B y   E l i s a b e t h   B e h r m a n n
-- 2010-10-04T20:12:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-04/academics-in-australia-win-16-pay-increase-over-3-years-review-reports.html
Australian academics at 28 out of 38
universities have won salary increases of at least 16 percent
over three years that will push the average salary of senior
lecturers to A$100,000 by mid-2012, the Australian Financial
Review reported, citing the National Tertiary Education Union.  To contact the reporter on this story:
